docs {
  ## Review a Purchase Request
  ส่งใบขอซื้อกลับตรวจสอบ ช่วยให้ผู้อนุมัติสามารถให้ข้อเสนอแนะหรือขอแก้ไขก่อนตัดสินใจอนุมัติหรือปฏิเสธ รองรับการตรวจสอบจัดซื้อแบบร่วมกัน Returns only items pending the requesting user's action / แสดงเฉพาะรายการที่รอการดำเนินการของผู้ใช้ปัจจุบัน

  Allows an approver to review a purchase request and provide feedback or modifications before making a final approve/reject decision, supporting collaborative procurement review.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Purchase request ID |

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `version` | string | No | latest | API version |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `procurement.purchase_request:view`
  - **Roles**: Requestor, HOD, Purchase, Approval

  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "stage_role": "review",
    "des_stage": "Please review the quantities",
    "details": []
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "pr_status": "reviewing"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid Bearer token |
  | 403 | User is not assigned to this approval stage |
  | 404 | Purchase request not found |
  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}

params:path {
  bu_code: {{bu_code}}
  id: {{pr_id}}
}
